The Garlic Network - Server side
================================

The Garlic network is a decentralized p2p network. Current status:
alpha & testing. You can read some information about concept of
network here:
	https://tin.mrrva.org/

Project modules
---------------

- Network:    Works with socket and some structs.
- Router:     Makes routes for connected clients and nodes.
- Storage:    Serves database and structures.
- Encryption: Encrypting network messages.

Requirements
------------

- sqlite3 (libsqlite3-dev)
- sodium (libsodium-dev)

